##################################################################
SET UP YOUR MACHINE TO FOLLOW THE " FASTER_RCNN_tuto_by_golden "
##################################################################


A couple of installations need to be done in order to avoid compatibility issue.

- set up a brand new virtual environment ( safety measure )
pip install --upgrade pip

sudo pip3 install -r Bureau/requirements-linux-python3.txt 
cd Documents/
mkdir my_tensorflow
cd my_tensorflow
python3 -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate

sudo apt-get install python3-pip python3-dev

-install tensorflow 
pip install tensorflow==1.13.2

-install keras
sudo pip3 install keras

-download and install labelIm
https://tzutalin.github.io/labelImg/

- install protocbuffer
pip3 install protobuf-compiler

sudo apt-get install libxml2-dev libxslt-dev python-dev
pip install lxml
pip install lxml==3.4.2


pip install pycocotools
sudo pip3 install matplotlib



pip install jupyterlab
cd Documents/models/research/object_detection
jupyter notebook


NB: Be ready to install other programs if needed.


